	(text "Bipolar +-15V for analog audio circuits.\nDC-DC isolated converter (e.g. TMA2415D or MEE3S2415SC) or\ntransformer-based with 7815/7915 linear post-regulators.\nOutput: +15V / -15V, typ 100-200mA per rail.\nDecoupling: 10uF + 100nF on each rail.\nKeep analog ground star-point separate from digital GND.\nSuitable for op-amp stages, audio preamps, sensor conditioning."
		(at 76.2 38.1 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.524 1.524)
			)
		)
